data.description: Come take a look at this beautiful 4 bedroom, 3 bath, 2 car garage just minutes from Ellsworth Air Force Base, and Douglas area school district. This ranch style home features an open concept with lots of natural light, and vaulted ceilings. Kitchen features stainless steel appliances with newly finished cabinets and an island for extra counter space and storage. Primary bedroom has trayed ceilings with a walk-in closet and personal bath. Large family room in the basement along with 2 very large 3rd and 4th bedrooms!
